# Voice Interview — End-to-End Flow Analysis

## Pipeline Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["🎙 VoiceInterviewLauncher<br/>Record / Upload audio"] -->|POST /voice-interviews| B["create_voice_interview<br/>Saves audio, creates VoiceInterview + ImportRun"]
    B -->|status: uploaded| C["VoiceProcessingProgress<br/>Polls GET /voice-interviews/:id"]
    C -->|status: transcribing| D["gpt-4o-transcribe<br/>(Whisper)"]
    D -->|transcript saved| E["status: extracting"]
    E --> F["BulkImportAIExtractor<br/>Text → BulkImportAIOutput"]
    F --> G["BulkImportService<br/>Build ImportItems with groupId"]
    G -->|status: review_ready| H["VoiceReviewWorkspace<br/>Groups + StreamCards"]
    H -->|User resolves groups| I["bulkImportAPI.finalize()"]
    I --> J["VoiceSuccessScreen<br/>Stats + suggestion CTA"]

    G -.->|items with no parent| K["OrphanStreamPicker<br/>(if companyLocations available)"]
    K -->|onAssign| L["bulkImportAPI.importOrphanProjects"]
```

---

