## What Works Well ✅

1. **Full upload pipeline** — record or upload → transcribe → extract → review (all automated)
2. **Split-panel review** — transcript + extracted data side by side, with evidence playback
3. **Group resolution** — RadioGroup (Map/Create/Reject) per location group
4. **Per-item actions** — Accept/Reject/Amend with inline editing and confidence chips
5. **Context-aware labels** — "Needs mapping" / "Wrong location" / "Needs review"
6. **Review notes visibility** — invalid items show amber explanation text
7. **Undo on reject** — toast with Undo button (awaits API before confirming)
8. **Skeleton loading** — pulse-animated cards match final layout
9. **Orphan rescue** — shared picker assigns unlinked streams to locations
10. **Backend fallback** — `stream_location_ref` match before marking invalid
11. **Retry on failure** — [retry](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/lib/api/voice-interviews.ts#77-89) endpoint + UI button for failed transcription/extraction
12. **Finalize → success** — creates projects, hydrates intake suggestions, shows CTA
13. **Audio/transcript retention** — time-limited, with purge service

---

## What's Missing / Gaps 🔍

### P0 — Functional gaps

| # | Gap | Impact | Effort |
|---|---|---|---|
| **1** | **No edit drawer** — [StreamCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/stream-card.tsx#54-252) has inline 2-field edit only. Bulk import has [EditItemDrawer](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/edit-item-drawer.tsx#48-213) with all fields, description, review notes, validation | Users can't fully correct AI errors before finalize | 2h — reuse [EditItemDrawer](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/edit-item-drawer.tsx#48-213) |
| **2** | **No "partial finalize" recovery** — if user finalized some groups then dismissed, re-opening shows all groups again (no awareness of which were already finalized) | Confusion on re-entry; may try to finalize already-done groups | 3h — filter items by status on load |
| **3** | **No progress indicator during finalize** — finalize button goes to loading spinner, no per-group progress | Anxiety on slow finalize with many groups | 1h — progress bar or per-group status |

### P1 — UX polish

| # | Gap | Impact | Effort |
|---|---|---|---|
| **4** | **"Map existing" doesn't have a location selector** — RadioGroup says "Map existing" but there's no dropdown to pick which existing location to map to | Map action is incomplete — user resolves as "map" but can't specify target | 2h — add location Select in resolver |
| **5** | **No batch operations** — no "Accept all" / "Reject all" per group | Tedious for groups with 10+ streams | 1h |
| **6** | **Dismissed orphan picker can't reopen** — once dismissed, no way to get it back in the session | One-time "dismiss" is destructive | 15m — add "Show unassigned" link |
| **7** | **No confidence threshold filtering** — no way to show only low-confidence items for focused review | Makes triage slower with many items | 1h |
| **8** | **`Loader2` still imported but unused** — after skeleton loading change, `Loader2` import is dead code | Minor lint issue | 5m |

### P2 — Backend improvements

| # | Gap | Impact | Effort |
|---|---|---|---|
| **9** | **No speaker diarization** — transcription uses Whisper plain, no speaker separation | Multi-person interviews lose attribution | API change (switch to speaker-aware model) |
| **10** | **No transcript editing** — user can't correct transcription errors before extraction | Garbage-in from bad transcription | 4h — new endpoint + UI panel |
| **11** | **No re-extraction from edited transcript** — even if we add transcript editing, no way to re-run extraction | Feature dependency on #10 | 2h — backend endpoint |

### P3 — Missing tests

| # | Gap | Effort |
|---|---|---|
| **12** | [OrphanStreamPicker](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/shared/orphan-stream-picker.tsx#40-203) — no unit test | 30m |
| **13** | [StreamCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/stream-card.tsx#54-252) — no render test for reviewNotes / statusLabel | 30m |
| **14** | Backend [location_ref](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/backend/app/services/bulk_import_ai_extractor.py#448-450) fallback — no integration test | 1h |
| **15** | [_statusLabel](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-workspace.tsx#62-78) with constants — no unit test for all branches | 15m |

